<html lang="sv">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<title>La Copa del Mundo 2026</title>
		<style is:global>
			@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@400;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');

			:root {
				--bg: #0a0e14;
				--card: #111825;
				--text: #f0f0f0;
				--muted: #8a9ab5;
				--yellow: #fecc02;
				--celeste: #75aadb;
			}

			* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
			html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

			body {
				font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
				background: var(--bg);
				color: var(--text);
				line-height: 1.6;
			}

			h1, h2, h3 {
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				text-transform: uppercase;
			}

			/* ---- HERO ---- */
			.hero {
				position: relative;
				height: 100vh;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				text-align: center;
				overflow: hidden;
			}

			.hero-bg {
				position: absolute;
				inset: 0;
				background: url('/forlan.jpg') center center / cover no-repeat;
				filter: brightness(0.3) saturate(1.2);
			}

			.hero-overlay {
				position: absolute;
				inset: 0;
				background: linear-gradient(
					to bottom,
					rgba(10, 14, 20, 0.2) 0%,
					rgba(10, 14, 20, 0.1) 50%,
					rgba(10, 14, 20, 0.9) 90%,
					rgba(10, 14, 20, 1) 100%
				);
			}

			.hero-content {
				position: relative;
				z-index: 1;
				padding: 2rem;
			}

			.hero h1 {
				font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
				font-weight: 700;
				line-height: 1;
				letter-spacing: 0.03em;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}

			.hero .sub {
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem);
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 0.15em;
				color: var(--muted);
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
				font-style: italic;
			}

			.cta {
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
				background: var(--yellow);
				color: var(--bg);
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				font-size: 1.15rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 0.05em;
				text-decoration: none;
				transition: all 0.2s;
			}

			.cta:hover {
				background: #fff;
				transform: translateY(-2px);
				box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(245, 197, 24, 0.2);
			}

			/* ---- SECTIONS ---- */
			.section {
				padding: 5rem 2rem;
				max-width: 800px;
				margin: 0 auto;
			}

			.section h2 {
				font-size: 2rem;
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
				color: var(--yellow);
			}

			.section-intro {
				color: var(--muted);
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
			}

			/* ---- STEPS ---- */
			.steps { display: grid; gap: 1.25rem; }

			.step {
				display: flex;
				gap: 1.5rem;
				align-items: flex-start;
				background: var(--card);
				padding: 1.75rem;
				border-left: 3px solid var(--celeste);
			}

			.step-num {
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				font-size: 2.2rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				color: var(--celeste);
				line-height: 1;
				flex-shrink: 0;
				width: 2rem;
				text-align: center;
			}

			.step h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
			.step p { color: var(--muted); }
			.step strong { color: var(--text); }

			/* ---- SWISH ---- */
			.swish-box {
				background: var(--card);
				padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
				text-align: center;
			}

			.swish-box h3 {
				font-size: 1.4rem;
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			.swish-box .amount {
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				font-size: 2.5rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				color: var(--yellow);
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}

			.swish-qr {
				background: #fff;
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 1rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}

			.swish-qr img {
				display: block;
				width: 200px;
				height: 200px;
			}

			.swish-btn {
				display: block;
				margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
				padding: 1rem 2rem;
				background: #4DAB3D;
				color: #fff;
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				font-size: 1.15rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 0.03em;
				text-decoration: none;
				border-radius: 40px;
				transition: all 0.2s;
				width: fit-content;
			}

			.swish-btn:hover {
				background: #3d9a2e;
				transform: translateY(-2px);
				box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(77, 171, 61, 0.3);
			}

			.swish-or {
				color: var(--muted);
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}

			.swish-hint {
				color: var(--muted);
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				margin-top: 0.5rem;
			}

			/* ---- PRIZES ---- */
			.prizes {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
				gap: 1.25rem;
				margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
			}

			.prize {
				background: var(--card);
				padding: 1.75rem 1.25rem;
				text-align: center;
			}

			.prize-place {
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				font-size: 1.3rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
			}

			.prize:nth-child(1) .prize-place { color: var(--yellow); }
			.prize:nth-child(2) .prize-place { color: var(--celeste); }
			.prize:nth-child(3) .prize-place { color: #cd7f32; }

			.prize:nth-child(1) { border-top: 3px solid var(--yellow); }
			.prize:nth-child(2) { border-top: 3px solid var(--celeste); }
			.prize:nth-child(3) { border-top: 3px solid #cd7f32; }

			.prize-pct {
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				font-size: 2.8rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				line-height: 1;
			}

			.prize-label { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.85rem; }

			.prize-example {
				background: var(--card);
				padding: 1.1rem;
				color: var(--muted);
				text-align: center;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
			}

			.prize-example strong { color: var(--text); }

			/* ---- PARTICIPANTS ---- */
			.participants-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(170px, 1fr));
				gap: 0.6rem;
			}

			.participant {
				background: var(--card);
				padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.7rem;
				font-weight: 500;
			}

			.participant .num {
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				color: var(--celeste);
				font-weight: 600;
			}

			.participant.empty {
				opacity: 0.2;
				border: 1px dashed var(--muted);
				background: transparent;
			}

			/* ---- LEADERBOARD ---- */
			.section-wide {
				max-width: 1200px;
			}

			.leaderboard-layout {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr;
				gap: 32px;
				align-items: start;
			}

			.leaderboard-loading {
				background: var(--card);
				border-radius: 4px;
				padding: 64px 24px;
				text-align: center;
				color: var(--muted);
				border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
			}

			/* Leaderboard rows — no table, div-based for full control */
			.lb-header {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr 80px;
				padding: 0 16px 12px;
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				font-size: 0.7rem;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 0.14em;
				color: var(--muted);
				border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
				margin-bottom: 4px;
			}

			.lb-header span:last-child { text-align: right; }

			.lb-row {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr 80px;
				align-items: center;
				margin-bottom: 2px;
				cursor: pointer;
				border-radius: 4px;
				overflow: hidden;
				background: var(--card);
				transition: transform 0.15s ease, background 0.2s ease;
			}

			.lb-row:hover {
				transform: scale(1.01);
				background: #172033;
			}

			.lb-row.selected {
				background: #172033;
				border-left: 3px solid var(--yellow);
			}

			.lb-pos {
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				font-size: 1.3rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				text-align: center;
				padding: 16px 0;
				color: var(--muted);
			}

			.lb-row.top1 .lb-pos {
				color: var(--bg);
				background: var(--yellow);
				font-size: 1.4rem;
			}

			.lb-row.top2 .lb-pos {
				color: var(--bg);
				background: var(--celeste);
			}

			.lb-row.top3 .lb-pos {
				color: var(--bg);
				background: #cd7f32;
			}

			.lb-team {
				padding: 12px 16px;
			}

			.lb-team-name {
				font-weight: 600;
				font-size: 0.95rem;
				transition: color 0.15s;
				line-height: 1.3;
			}

			.lb-row:hover .lb-team-name,
			.lb-row.selected .lb-team-name {
				color: var(--yellow);
			}

			.lb-manager {
				font-size: 0.75rem;
				color: var(--muted);
				margin-top: 1px;
			}

			.lb-score {
				text-align: right;
				padding: 12px 16px;
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				font-size: 1.15rem;
				font-weight: 600;
			}

			.lb-score.positive { color: #22c55e; }
			.lb-score.zero { color: var(--muted); }

			.leaderboard-info {
				margin-top: 16px;
				font-size: 0.7rem;
				color: var(--muted);
				opacity: 0.4;
				text-align: right;
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				letter-spacing: 0.08em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
			}

			.leaderboard-pages {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
				gap: 6px;
				margin-top: 20px;
			}

			.leaderboard-pages button {
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				padding: 6px 14px;
				background: transparent;
				color: var(--muted);
				border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
				border-radius: 4px;
				cursor: pointer;
				transition: all 0.15s ease;
			}

			.leaderboard-pages button:hover {
				color: var(--text);
				border-color: var(--celeste);
			}

			.leaderboard-pages button.active {
				color: var(--bg);
				background: var(--yellow);
				border-color: var(--yellow);
				font-weight: 700;
			}

			/* ---- TEAM PANEL ---- */
			.team-panel {
				position: sticky;
				top: 24px;
				background: linear-gradient(165deg, #111825 0%, #0d1320 100%);
				border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
				border-radius: 4px;
				overflow: hidden;
			}

			.team-panel-empty {
				text-align: center;
				color: var(--muted);
				padding: 64px 24px;
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				line-height: 1.7;
			}

			.team-panel-empty .arrow {
				font-size: 1.8rem;
				margin-bottom: 8px;
				display: block;
				opacity: 0.3;
			}

			.tp-header {
				padding: 24px 24px 20px;
				border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(254,204,2,0.04) 0%, transparent 60%);
			}

			.tp-header h3 {
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				margin-bottom: 2px;
				letter-spacing: 0.02em;
			}

			.tp-header .tp-manager {
				color: var(--muted);
				font-size: 0.8rem;
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				letter-spacing: 0.04em;
			}

			.tp-section {
				padding: 20px 24px;
			}

			.tp-section + .tp-section {
				border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
			}

			.tp-section-title {
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				font-size: 0.65rem;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 0.16em;
				color: var(--celeste);
				margin-bottom: 12px;
			}

			.tp-player {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
				gap: 10px;
				align-items: center;
				padding: 8px 0;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
			}

			.tp-player:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

			.tp-pos-badge {
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				font-size: 0.6rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				letter-spacing: 0.06em;
				padding: 3px 6px;
				border-radius: 3px;
				text-align: center;
				min-width: 36px;
				color: var(--text);
				background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
			}

			.tp-pos-badge.mv { background: rgba(117,170,219,0.2); color: var(--celeste); }
			.tp-pos-badge.anf { background: rgba(254,204,2,0.15); color: var(--yellow); }

			.tp-player-name {
				font-weight: 500;
			}

			.tp-player .captain {
				color: var(--bg);
				background: var(--yellow);
				font-size: 0.6rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				margin-left: 6px;
				padding: 2px 5px;
				border-radius: 3px;
				vertical-align: 1px;
			}

			.tp-player-club {
				color: var(--muted);
				font-size: 0.75rem;
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				letter-spacing: 0.04em;
				text-align: right;
			}

			.tp-round {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
				gap: 12px;
				align-items: center;
				padding: 6px 0;
			}

			.tp-round-num {
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				font-size: 0.8rem;
				color: var(--muted);
				min-width: 20px;
			}

			.tp-round-bar {
				height: 6px;
				border-radius: 3px;
				background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
				overflow: hidden;
			}

			.tp-round-bar-fill {
				height: 100%;
				border-radius: 3px;
				transition: width 0.4s ease;
			}

			.tp-round-bar-fill.pos { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #22c55e, #4ade80); }
			.tp-round-bar-fill.neg { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ef4444, #f87171); }

			.tp-round-val {
				font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				min-width: 60px;
				text-align: right;
			}

			.tp-round-val.pos { color: #22c55e; }
			.tp-round-val.neg { color: #ef4444; }

			.tp-loading {
				text-align: center;
				color: var(--muted);
				padding: 64px 24px;
				font-size: 0.85rem;
			}

			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				.leaderboard-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
				.section-wide { max-width: 800px; }
				.lb-row:hover { transform: none; }
			}

			/* ---- TIKTOKS ---- */
			.tiktoks {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
				gap: 1.5rem;
				justify-items: center;
			}

			/* ---- PHOTO BREAK ---- */
			.photo-break {
				position: relative;
				height: 60vh;
				min-height: 350px;
				overflow: hidden;
			}

			.photo-break-bg {
				position: absolute;
				inset: 0;
				background-size: cover;
				background-position: center;
				background-repeat: no-repeat;
				background-attachment: fixed;
				filter: brightness(0.4) saturate(1.2);
			}

			.photo-break-overlay {
				position: absolute;
				inset: 0;
				background: linear-gradient(
					to bottom,
					rgba(10, 14, 20, 1) 0%,
					rgba(10, 14, 20, 0) 15%,
					rgba(10, 14, 20, 0) 85%,
					rgba(10, 14, 20, 1) 100%
				);
			}

			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				.photo-break-bg {
					background-attachment: scroll;
				}
				.photo-break { height: 40vh; min-height: 250px; }
			}

			/* ---- DIVIDER ---- */
			.divider {
				max-width: 800px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				border: none;
				border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
			}

			/* ---- FOOTER ---- */
			footer {
				text-align: center;
				padding: 3rem 2rem;
				border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
				color: var(--muted);
				font-size: 0.85rem;
			}

			footer strong { color: var(--text); }

			@media (max-width: 640px) {
				.prizes { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
				.step { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
				.section { padding: 3rem 1.25rem; }
				.tiktoks { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>

		<section class="hero">
			<div class="hero-bg"></div>
			<div class="hero-overlay"></div>
			<div class="hero-content">
				<h1>La Copa del Mundo 2026</h1>
				<p class="sub">En mot en, alla mot alla</p>
				<a href="#how" class="cta">Gå med</a>
				<a href="#leaderboard" class="cta" style="background: var(--celeste); margin-left: 12px;">Tabell</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section" id="how">
			<h2>Så funkar det</h2>
			<p class="section-intro">Tre steg, sen är du med.</p>
			<div class="steps">
				<div class="step">
					<div class="step-num">1</div>
					<div>
						<h3>Skapa ditt lag</h3>
						<p>Gå till Aftonbladets <strong>VM-elvan</strong> och skapa ditt lag. Välj spelare, sätt din startelva, och tävla baserat på verklig matchstatistik.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="step">
					<div class="step-num">2</div>
					<div>
						<h3>Swisha 300 kr</h3>
						<p>Skicka <strong>300 kr</strong> till Ruy via Swish: <strong>+46 70 306 42 11</strong>. Skriv ditt VM-elvan-lagnamn i meddelandet.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="step">
					<div class="step-num">3</div>
					<div>
						<h3>Du är med!</h3>
						<p>När vi fått ditt lagnamn och betalning dyker du upp i deltagarlistan. Gå med i <a href="https://chat.whatsapp.com/LGL6yZKMdtl7GTJKZrEKeX" target="_blank" style="color: var(--celeste); text-decoration: underline;">WhatsApp-gruppen</a> för uppdateringar och snack. Avspark <strong>11 juni</strong>.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<div class="photo-break">
			<div class="photo-break-bg" style="background-image: url('/suarez.jpg');"></div>
			<div class="photo-break-overlay"></div>
		</div>

		<section class="section" id="swish">
			<h2>Betala</h2>
			<p class="section-intro">Swisha insatsen direkt.</p>
			<div class="swish-box">
				<h3>Insats</h3>
				<div class="amount">300 kr</div>

				<a class="swish-btn"
					href="swish://payment?data=%7B%22version%22%3A1%2C%22payee%22%3A%7B%22value%22%3A%22%2B46703064211%22%2C%22editable%22%3Afalse%7D%2C%22amount%22%3A%7B%22value%22%3A300%2C%22editable%22%3Afalse%7D%2C%22message%22%3A%7B%22value%22%3A%22La%20Copa%20del%20Mundo%202026%22%2C%22editable%22%3Atrue%7D%7D">
					Öppna Swish
				</a>

				<p class="swish-or">eller skanna QR-koden</p>

				<div class="swish-qr">
					<img src="/api/swish-qr" alt="Swish QR-kod — 300 kr till Ruy" />
				</div>
				<p class="swish-hint">Till: Ruy (+46 70 306 42 11) &bull; Meddelande fylls i automatiskt</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<hr class="divider" />

		<section class="section">
			<h2>Potten</h2>
